{"tid":1375421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 支援車長罷工，集思廣益，講得唔岩請大大力屌","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:30.000Z","uid":164420,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfe54a8d4f4e5295b6acf58a8084d87d337d3be","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0PGQa1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0PGQa1.png&h=32d98e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成撚日9叫車長罷工，你地唔罷俾我睇？為飯碗邊個會罷？唔撚驚秋後算賬？<br />\n之前有個P牌Post「港鐵車長 將會係今次輸贏嘅關鍵」真係屌⋯⋯P牌都醒撚過你地班罷工膠。總結佢個Post加自己消化，真係有得諗：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每人月捐一舊水，基本盤200萬人就每月2億</span></span></strong>，未計海外眾籌，都絕對養得起500個月薪萬五六嘅港鐵車長。一人一舊，匿名冇負擔，輕鬆又簡單，效果好有望遍地開花，唔撚洗個個禮拜行得咁辛苦，就可以癱瘓半個香港，我唔撚信柒鵝唔腳軟唔回應。<br />\n<br />\n「罷工港鐵車長支援基金」類似612人道支援基金，失業救濟金之類。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不存在「煽動車長罷工」嘅動機</span></span>（有都係曲）如車長合理訴求被打壓，要罷工/辭職但冇飯開，香港人會施以「援手」咁解。如車長俾港鐵Black List永不錄用，或被民事起訴，就支持佢直到轉行/搵到新工或打官司。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌數字越多，想罷工嘅車長信心就大，最好<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">每日公布最新眾籌數字</span></span>。吸引更多「被壓迫嘅車長」加入罷工或集體辭職。趁咁撚多車長開名聯署，佢地多少都有被炒魷嘅準備，打鐵趁熱，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要趁車長同港鐵未傾掂數之前公開宣傳</span></span>，正式運作。預計初期未必有太大迴響，但港鐵車長聯署，眾籌幫手罷工單嘢炒起咗，證實眾籌有效支持罷工，有信心，其他行業跟風機會好大，更多人肯課金，基金個Pool都會瞬間膨脹，可能迅速蔓延到更多基層行業。<br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜同佢衝，唔係長久之計；眾籌世界登報，雷聲大雨點小，冇乜實質作用，變吓陣冇壞。要籌旗就籌比香港人，對準權貴，先撼動到政權。成立眾籌基金嘅具體框架同疑問，大家一齊諗一齊傾。即管屌，但真係要快！<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉！"},{"pid":"fb818af87807c6029ac4c5ea1b46bd59368a938b","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"445564fd0da9a9d3ca251c6a87e46f92dedfad3f","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"d00a42369a21a2802deb5d07188ab5f2c954db6e","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a402af51503d616baf798241bb9a839b8049fe","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d265d984cf8c8db9977c915320ba1a3a4c41025","tid":1375421,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2db18e2a0292300c26717137643b80d4244abf3","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"罷工撚同我入黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4db1195ebe2a4390448f2ea1a0c6ca95405f8ac","tid":1375421,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295d150fd32abd7cf668fd9f798709a60e5b2c61","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"鍵戰組，眾籌組，罷工撚，車長，入黎集思廣益！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73d2527ac1441c1afe3f321e549c3b790e168c6","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1974b1652c5c2050d24c36794024a9a52e2a2a6","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3a477613f619f4225604d371ca27e6c87dbdbfe","tid":1375421,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153f0be5806f9a4927c5e21a8108b402f0e7e48c","tid":1375421,"uid":143124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c4c5afbcfe830729ab1843619ced01dda1d25a3","tid":1375421,"uid":176164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"最好就係直接1-2日全日維修啦<br />\n你地話平時得果2個鐘整到唔多野<br />\n同都咁多年<br />\n係時候大維修"},{"pid":"80d9ccca80889bf27ea8c3573eff93e47c17c728","tid":1375421,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:30.000Z","msg":"認真，有邊個想返工丫？ 有邊個唔想罷工丫？<br />\n<br />\n但香港人最驚係冇左份工，冇錢冇收入。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果我地可以眾籌幫車長捱過難關，咁先可以成功推動罷工！<br />\n<br />\n有錢就有底氣，冇錢就乜都假，香港人最撚現實架！"}]}